---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Legal Notice"
  description="Legal notice and privacy information for otvt.fr, Olivier Thévet's web studio."
  pageKey="legal"
>
  <section class="pt-28 pb-20 sm:pb-28 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <div
        class="border border-vert/20 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-surface shadow-sm"
        data-reveal
      >
        <div
          class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 sm:px-5 py-3 border-b border-vert/10 bg-surface-alt"
        >
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ff5f56]"></span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ffbd2e]"></span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#28c840]"></span>
          <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-ink/70 font-medium"
            >olivier@otvt:~/legal</span
          >
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 sm:px-12 py-8 sm:py-14">
          <p
            class="text-xs text-vert/85 font-mono mb-8 sm:mb-10 leading-relaxed"
          >
            <span class="text-vert font-semibold">olivier@otvt</span>:<span
              class="text-jaune">~</span
            ><span class="text-ink/70">$ </span><span
              class="text-ink/70" data-typewriter>cat legal-notice.txt</span
            >
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.15em] text-vert/85 uppercase mb-6"
          >
            Legal
          </p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-ink">
            Legal Notice
          </h1>

          <div
            class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-sm text-ink/70 leading-relaxed"
          >
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink mb-2">
                Publisher
              </h2>
              <p>
                <strong class="text-ink">Olivier Thévet</strong><br />
                Sole trader (French micro-entreprise)<br />
                Origny le Sec, Aube (10)<br />
                France
              </p>
              <p class="mt-2">
                Email: <a
                  href="mailto:contact@otvt.fr"
                  class="text-vert underline decoration-vert/40 underline-offset-2 hover:text-vert/85 transition-colors"
                  >contact@otvt.fr</a
                >
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink mb-2">
                Hosting
              </h2>
              <p>
                <strong class="text-ink">Netlify, Inc.</strong><br />
                101 2nd Street<br />
                San Francisco, CA 94105<br />
                USA<br />
                <a
                  href="https://www.netlify.com"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="text-vert underline decoration-vert/40 underline-offset-2 hover:text-vert/85 transition-colors"
                  >netlify.com</a
                >
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink mb-2">
                Intellectual property
              </h2>
              <p>
                All content on this site (text, graphics, source code) is
                the property of Olivier Thévet unless stated otherwise. Any
                reproduction, distribution or use without authorization is
                prohibited.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink mb-2">
                Liability
              </h2>
              <p>
                The information provided on this site is for general
                guidance only. Olivier Thévet cannot guarantee the accuracy
                or completeness of this information. Use of the site is at
                the user's own risk.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink mb-2">
                Data protection (GDPR)
              </h2>
              <p>
                Personal data collected through the contact form (name,
                email, message) is used solely to respond to your inquiry.
                It is never sold, shared or used for commercial purposes.
              </p>
              <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
                <li>Retention period: 3 years after the last contact.</li>
                <li>
                  You can request the deletion of your data at any time by
                  email.
                </li>
                <li>
                  No cookies are set on this site. The client area (see
                  below) uses the browser's <code>localStorage</code> to keep
                  you signed in — this is not a cookie, and is strictly
                  necessary for a feature you opt into by logging in.
                </li>
                <li>
                  The contact form is processed by the third-party provider
                  <a
                    href="https://web3forms.com"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="text-vert underline decoration-vert/40 underline-offset-2 hover:text-vert/85 transition-colors"
                    >Web3Forms</a
                  >, which forwards your message by email without storing
                  it long-term.
                </li>
              </ul>
              <p class="mt-3">
                For any question about your data: <a
                  href="mailto:contact@otvt.fr"
                  class="text-vert underline decoration-vert/40 underline-offset-2 hover:text-vert/85 transition-colors"
                  >contact@otvt.fr</a
                >
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink mb-2">
                Client area
              </h2>
              <p>
                The client area (login, project tracking, invoices,
                messaging) processes data necessary to perform our
                contractual relationship, not on the basis of consent.
              </p>
              <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
                <li>
                  Data involved: login email, project information, invoices
                  (and the information they contain). The client area's
                  message form works just like the public contact form (see
                  above): no history is stored within the client area
                  itself.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Sub-processor: <a
                    href="https://supabase.com"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="text-vert underline decoration-vert/40 underline-offset-2 hover:text-vert/85 transition-colors"
                    >Supabase Inc.</a
                  >, with data hosted in the European Union.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Passwordless login (one-time login code sent by email),
                  access to your data is technically restricted at the
                  database level (each client can only query their own
                  data), encryption in transit (TLS).
                </li>
                <li>
                  Unusual sign-in detection: when you sign in from a device
                  or browser we don't recognize, we keep a technical
                  fingerprint (derived from your browser and IP address, not
                  the raw values) and send you a notification email. This
                  data is used solely for security purposes and never for
                  anything else.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Retention period: invoices are subject to statutory
                  accounting retention obligations (around 10 years under
                  French law) and cannot be deleted before that period, even
                  on request. Project data and messages are kept for the
                  duration of the contractual relationship, then 3 years
                  after the last contact.
                </li>
                <li>
                  You can export your project, invoice and message data at
                  any time from your client area ("Export my data" button),
                  or request deletion of your account and data ("Request
                  account deletion" button — we'll get back to you within
                  48h), within the limits of the invoice retention
                  obligation.
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
